Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.avltree

Class AvlTreeNode

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.avltree.AvlTreeNode
public class AvlTreeNode extends Object

Title: AvlTreeNode

Description:

Class for creating individual nodes in the AVL tree. Note that there are parent, left, and right attributes which are used to set the structure of the tree.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
